data.description:
Great Location! Versatile Living Space! 
Welcome to this charming home with a fantastic location! Originally designed as a 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence, this property offers a unique and flexible layout that caters to various living arrangements.Explore the possibilities and make this home your own - whether it's a spacious family home or a residence with a separate living unit. The choice is yours! The master bedroom and laundry room have been thoughtfully converted into a separate apartment/mother-in-law suite. This independent space boasts its own kitchen and laundry facilities, providing an ideal solution for multi-generational living or a potential rental opportunity. 
Enjoy the convenience of a private entrance and a designated entryway for the additional living space. This setup ensures privacy and autonomy for both the main home and the separate suite. 
Looking to revert to the original floor plan? No worries! This home is designed with flexibility in mind, and the master bedroom suite can be effortlessly converted back to restore the home to its original 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom layout.
